    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>High-speed ground transportation vehicles traveling along guideways using superconducting devices of various configurations, generally with the aid of magnetic forces and linear induction.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vehículo de transporte terrestre de alta velocidad que viaja a lo largo de vías guiadas utilizando dispositivos superconductores de varias configuraciones, generalmente con la ayuda de fuerzas magnéticas e inducción linear.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ultrasnel openbaar vervoer dat langs banen loopt met gebruik van verschillende typen supergeleidende apparaten, meestal met behulp van magnetische krachten en lineaire inductie.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hochgeschwindigkeitsfahrzeug zu Lande, das entlang einer Führungsbahn fährt und dabei supraleitende Geräte verschiedener Art nutzt, meist mithilfe von magnetischer Kraft und linearer Induktion.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
